@_SharonThornton @BigBadDenis @CollignonPeter @Globalbiosec @CrabbBrendan You can’t be “on top” of data that is being kept secret.

A source of immense frustration to @CrabbBrendan, @Globalbiosec (and even @CollignonPeter) I am sure.

The stuff above had to be picked out of the text of various reports.

@BigBadDenis @CollignonPeter I think @CollignonPeter has confused two concepts here.

Zero-Covid was something many originally hoped could be achieved through a combination of vaccines and airborne disease mitigations.

Those who ignored mitigations pretty much destroyed any hope of achieving Zero-Covid.
